      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. To make the tension even more realistic, I need to describe the people moving through the scene. Can you add a few more details about the types of people walking these streets? I want to show the specific kind of crowd that makes a person feel like they're in a high-crime area—the kind of people you'd see loitering on corners or looking suspicious in this kind of neighborhood.",
